text: Butterbean's Café is an American-Irish computer-animated culinary fantasy children's television series created by Jonny Belt and Robert Scull (who both also created Bubble Guppies) and ordered by Nickelodeon. The series ran November 12, 2018 to November 1, 2020, with 2 seasons and 60 episodes.
